Jetsunma Tenzin Palmo pɩkɛ pʊda Ɛsɔ sɛtʊ hɩɖɛ naɖɩyɛ, ɖɩ-tɛ nɛ Drukpa tɛ kiŋ kɛ Kagyu sukuli taa. Vicki Mackenzie, ɛnʊ mana se Cave in the Snow kɛ ɛ-hɔɔlʊʊ taa, ɛtɔŋ se ndʊ  tiyeba nɛ ɛma ɛ-takayaɣ kɩkalaɣ yɔ lɛ se kalɩ Tenzin Palmo tɔm kɛ pʊda  Ɛsɔ sɛtʊ ŋgbɛyɛ takayaɣ. 

Malaba tambaɣ se mantalɩ lɔŋ ɖeɖe ɛzɩ halʊ nɛ mambafɛyɩ paa halɩ weziŋ ɛzɩma pɩkpaɣkɩ-m kɔyɔ. Jetsunma tɩyɩna-tʊ, ɛkɛ wɩlɩyʊ halɩñɩnʊ nɛ ɛnʊ ɖʊna Dongyu Gatsal Ling tɛ Ɛsɔ sɛtʊ ŋgbɛyɛ Himachal Pradesh Ɛndɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa. 

Patɩla-ɩ sakɩyɛ mbʊ pʊyɔɔ yɔ ɛkɛ yogini waa taa halʊ kɛ wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʊyɛ taa nɛ ɛtana-tʊ Wɩsɩ ɖɩlɩyɛ taa ajɛyɛ taa yɔ, ɛɛwɛ kisinziku nakʊyʊ tɛɛ lakʊ taa kɛnɛ halɩ ɛla peeɖe pɩnzɩ 12, Himalaya  pʊʊ sɔsɔŋ yɔɔ nɛ pɩnzɩ nzɩ sɩ-tɛ hiu nɛ naalɛ taa lɛ, ɛmʊ piŋ pɩnzɩ naadozo.
